        </p>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8 text-customgray leading-relaxed">
          Your regular donation ensures these vulnerable children grow up safe, supported, and with dignity. You're not just changing a life you're shaping a future.
        </p>

        <!-- Key Points -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-8">
          <div
            class="bg-customblue/5 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-customblue"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="bg-customblue/10 p-3 rounded-full text-customblue">
                <i class="fas fa-heart-broken"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Why Orphan Sponsorship Matters</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-customgray">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-circle text-xs mt-1.5 text-hotpink"></i>
                <span>Millions of children live without parents or stable care</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-circle text-xs mt-1.5 text-hotpink"></i>
                <span>Sponsorship provides daily meals, school, and medical aid</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-circle text-xs mt-1.5 text-hotpink"></i>
                <span>A supported child has a better chance at a strong, healthy future</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-teal/5 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-teal">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="bg-teal/10 p-3 rounded-full text-teal">
                <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">How Your Sadaqah Helps</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-customgray">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-circle text-xs mt-1.5 text-hotpink"></i>
                <span>Covers education, nutrition, clothing, and healthcare</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-circle text-xs mt-1.5 text-hotpink"></i>
                <span>Supports emotional well-being and social development</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-circle text-xs mt-1.5 text-hotpink"></i>
                <span>Helps orphans thrive in trusted homes or care programs</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-hotpink/5 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-hotpink">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="bg-hotpink/10 p-3 rounded-full text-hotpink">
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Why My Sadaqah Online?</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-customgray">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-circle text-xs mt-1.5 text-customblue"></i>
                <span>Simple and secure monthly giving</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-circle text-xs mt-1.5 text-customblue"></i>
                <span>100% donation policy your full gift goes to the child</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-circle text-xs mt-1.5 text-customblue"></i>
                <span>Regular updates so you see the difference you're making</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

